      <profileDesc>
        <abstract>
            <p>A text in part composed of homilies, divided into readings
               for each month of the year,
               describing the life and death of John the Baptist.
                 It seems to be a rare composition, and it
                  is different from a work of a similar structure
                 contained in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp007">Gulo Maḵadā, ʾƎndā Ḥawāryāt Ṗeṭros wa-Ṗāwlos, EHPP-007</ref>, and another one
                 in the edition
                 <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/VNQUDS5T"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Tarraqan2003GadlaYohannes"/><title level="m">ገድለ ዮሐንስ መጥምቅ በግእዝና በአማርኛ &lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;(&lt;/hi&gt;Gadla Yoḥannǝs Maṭmǝq bagǝʾǝzǝnnā baʾamārǝññā).&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, ‘The Acts of John the Baptist, in Gǝʾǝz and Amharic’)&lt;/hi&gt;</title><editor><t:name xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Makwannǝn Ambarbar Śǝgate, &lt;i&gt;Malʿaka bǝrhānāt&lt;/i&gt;</t:name></editor><pubPlace>ʾAddis ʾAbabā</pubPlace><publisher>n.pub.</publisher><date>2003</date></bibl>.</p>
        </abstract>
